S: Ijapokuwa;
TS: ulisema kwamba atakaye kuomba kitu chochote utamupa, ninakuomba Baba,
:/: mwisho wangu uwe mzuri, nifikie kumaliza mwendo wangu, ni pumuzike shida zote :/:

Fr. Enock SHIMIYE, Kyeshero

