450.B.UBW’ UMWAMI YES’ AZAZA 3/4
1.Ubw’ UmwamI Yes’ azaza Kwend’ abo yatoye,
Ab’ akunda b’ abatoni, Bamuyobotse.

Bazaka nk’ Inyenyeri Zitatse kw’ikamba rye; 
Bazatangaza cyane, Bakize rwose.

2.Ubw’ azaz’ akorany’ abo Yatoye ba hose,
Bera baboneye rwose, B’abatoni be.

3.Yemwe bantu, yemwe bantu Bakund’ Umukiza,
Ni mw’ akunda, nimw’ akunda Nk’ abatoni be.

