Ndiyo maana yeye alisema, 
Bila mimi hamuna uwezo             
Wa kumushinda  Yule muovu x2
Fr. David Muganza  M.  -    RUMBA


668.A.UNIANGALIE  ATWAMBIA 4/4
1.Uniangalie atwambia, 
Yesu aliye tufia;  
Musalabani ni uzima ; 
Hapa utaipata hazina.

Kutazama kalvari (2x)
Ni kupewa kuishi, 
Kuutazama muti (wa Kalvari).

2.Ninapo jaribiwa gafula, 
Shetani hatanitega; 
Nikitazama musalaba, 
Nguvu nitaipata kwa Bwana.

3.Musalaba nitautazama, 
Kila wakati daima. 
Ahadi nitategemea, 
Hivi kabisa sita-anguka.

Amelia M. Hull, There is life for a look at the cricified one, 
