Nkuko wasezeranye 
Twumva twumye mu mitima : Uduhembuz’ imvura

Utuvubir’ imvura, Iy’ umugisha wawe !Hahore hagw’ urujojo :
Duh’ umuvumbi wawe !

2.Mwam’ utuvubir’ imvura: Yaduhembura rwose
Twumva mu matw’ irahinda : Uyidusohozeho !

3.Mwam’ utuvubir’ imvura, Iducunshumukeho !
Tuje guhabg’ umugisha Wadusezeranije.

4.Mwam’ utuvubir’ imvura : 
Icyamp’ ikagwa vuba, 
Ubu tukiri ku mavi, Tukigutakambira ! 

